{
  "stem": "3100.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "No one was to embrace us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, well, get married.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, well, we'll think about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, of course, on September the 1st, 1945, just six years after the war broke out, we married.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We found where there was a Rabbi came back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He wasn't a Rabbi, he was a [? shulkat. ?] But he married us there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We invited all those people who came back from camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't remember how many-- 50, 60 of them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had-- we didn't know where, but we found a lonslady who had a bigger house from her mother and father left.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So, we married there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And if I could tell you that after almost 50 years, we've went back to visit all the camps.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We went back because I didn't have a place where to go to visit the graves of my parents or relatives.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my wife didn't have a place where to go to visit her parents.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she sort of figured out that they have gone to Czestochowa.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And all the people in Czestochowa were taken to Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we took our family, our daughter, and her husband and our two sons and their spouses, and we went back to Poland to visit all the camps.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if there was one trip that I undertook, I know it was very painful for us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I felt that I walk in to a camp as a free man.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that I could walk out whenever I want.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when we came to Treblinka, my wife felt that she came to like a place of a cemetery because it was only a mountain of ashes there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there we saw the crematoriums.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if you don't see the place, you can't envision how the camp looked.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
